IMPOSED AND STAYED SENTENCE OF:   

9 MONTHS JAIL;

TERM OF PROBATION:  1 YEAR;

CONDITIONS OF PROBATION:  

*Maintain full time employment and/or combination of schooling 
*No violent contact with: the victim.
*DNA sample to be provided if not yet previously done.
*Follow through with any treatment and/or counseling recommended by Agent;
*Mental Heath evaluation and treatment deemed appropriate.
*No possession of any weapons.
*Perform 75 hours community service.

RESTITUTION:  set at zero;

COURT COSTS:  $243.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

DNA SURCHARGE:  $200.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

CONDITION TIME:30 Days, non working hours, last 25 days STAYED; to be used at agent's discretion.  Agent to determine with or without non working hours.  Defendant to report by Monday, November 9, 2015 by 12:00 p.m. (apply 1 day credit to the first 5 days).

  Expunction is conditionally granted upon verification of completion of sentence, payment of all costs/fees and no new criminal law violations.
